        Product Description

        When you're seeking a seamless, high-quality audio experience, the 2nd Gen AirPods with Charging Case from Apple are more magical than ever. These sleek and modern wireless headphones offer extended talk time, voice-activated Siri access, and come with an innovative charging case.

        The moment you take them out, they're ready to sync with all your Apple devices. Place them in your ears and they connect instantly, immersing you in rich, high-fidelity sound. Their wireless functionality is at its peak, with a simple one-tap setup that keeps your AirPods automatically on and always connected.

        These high-tech AirPods are intuitive, sensing when they're in your ears and pausing playback when you remove them. The AirPods experience remains consistent whether you're using them with your iPhone, Apple Watch, iPad, or Mac.

        Interacting with Siri, your favorite personal assistant, is easier than ever. Just say "Hey Siri" for hands-free assistance, no need to reach for your iPhone. Powered by the all-new Apple H1 headphone chip, these AirPods deliver a faster, more stable wireless connection to your devices. This results in up to 2x faster switching between active devices and a 1.5x faster connection time for phone calls.

        The H1 chip also enables voice-activated Siri access and delivers up to 30 percent lower gaming latency. Whether you're gaming, listening to music, or enjoying podcasts, you'll experience superior sound quality.

        The AirPods are equipped with optical sensors and motion accelerometers that work together to automatically control the audio experience. They engage the microphones for phone calls and Siri access, and enable sound playback as soon as they're in your ears. You have the freedom to wear one or both AirPods, and can easily control playback with a double-tap.

        A speech-detecting accelerometer recognizes when you're speaking and works in tandem with a pair of beamforming microphones to filter out external noise and focus on your voice.

        The AirPods offer an impressive 24-hour battery life, delivering up to 5 hours of listening time and 3 hours of talk time on a single charge. The charging case holds multiple charges for more than 24 hours of listening time. Need a quick charge? Just 15 minutes in the case gives you up to 3 hours of listening time and 2 hours of talk time.

        Checking the battery is as simple as holding the AirPods next to your iPhone or asking Siri "How's the battery on my AirPods?" Instant setup and easy listening make these AirPods the perfect companion for your Apple devices. Simply choose AirPods on your Mac or iPad for easy setup and magical results.

        How customer reviews and ratings work

        Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

        To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.
